# Clawkie-Talkie client env template.
#
# Copy to `client/.env.local` and edit. Vite loads these at dev/build
# time; only variables prefixed `VITE_` are exposed to browser code.
#
# No variables are currently required. The phone client reads the
# daemon's PeerJS host ID from the URL (`?host=<id>`); signaling goes
# through the public PeerJS broker (peerjs.com), no per-user config.
